[   13.715167] to a HARDIRQ-irq-unsafe lock:
[   13.722426]  (&ctl->lock){+.+.}-{2:2}
[   13.722430]
[   13.722430] ... which became HARDIRQ-irq-unsafe at:
[   13.732319] ...
[   13.732324]   lock_acquire+0xec/0x368
[   13.735985]   _raw_spin_lock+0x60/0x88
